Text: Evaluator Training Cc Gentlemen We need your coding in order to pay for the training classwe split between the two groups Total cost was Cliff McPherson

OQ Evaluator Class Cc Ive arranged for Debbie Midgley from VeriForce to provide the training on January from AM until PM This class is for the personnel who will evaluate the skills of other personnel Maximum class size is Please let me know if Ive missed Houston or Midland based personnel in the distribution list Dale Can you reserve a conference room on your floor for the day Weve called people and cant seem to connect with the person in charge Thanks

CFR regs OQ Rule referencesWe are ordering hard copies of the regs as you requested but in the mean time you can read the official text at the following web site cfrparthtm For gas OQ is addressed near the end of the file at CFR Subpart N cfrparthtm For oil look for the OQ Rule at CFR Subpart G also near the end of the document
